Semi-Automatic System Classification

SACS

Description: Document classification for the European Commission using keywords extraction and taxonomy classification.

Role: I worked in a professional team as a Solutions Assistant at NTTDATA.

Technologies: Angular, Spring, Semantic Web...

Duration: +9 months.

About me

My name is Iker and I am 20. I am a second year student of Software Development and IT. I worked 6 months as an intern in NTTDATA, a huge company. I have been able to complete a lot of projects, thanks to dedicating more than +1500 hours in development.
